{
  "video_id": "vWJwa7lntTs",
  "title": "A video game to cope with grief | Amy Green",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12772.0,
      "end_time": 16956.0,
      "text": "Two months ago, my kids and I huddled around a cell phone"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16980.0,
      "end_time": 19276.0,
      "text": "watching the live stream of the Game Awards,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19300.0,
      "end_time": 22196.0,
      "text": "one of the video game industry&#39;s biggest nights."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 22220.0,
      "end_time": 25875.0,
      "text": "They announced the nominees for the Game for Impact,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 25900.0,
      "end_time": 28956.0,
      "text": "an award that&#39;s given to a thought-provoking video game"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 28980.0,
      "end_time": 32756.0,
      "text": "with a profound prosocial message or meaning."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 32780.0,
      "end_time": 34476.0,
      "text": "They opened the envelope"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 34500.0,
      "end_time": 37716.0,
      "text": "and they read the title of our video game."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 37740.0,
      "end_time": 39116.0,
      "text": "An award ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 39140.0,
      "end_time": 40956.0,
      "text": "for impact."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 40980.0,
      "end_time": 42675.0,
      "text": "It was almost funny, actually,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 42700.0,
      "end_time": 45356.0,
      "text": "because I always thought that winning an award like that"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 45380.0,
      "end_time": 48360.0,
      "text": "would have this huge impact on my life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 48600.0,
      "end_time": 50820.0,
      "text": "but I found that the opposite is true."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 51660.0,
      "end_time": 53750.0,
      "text": "The big nights,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 53100.0,
      "end_time": 55196.0,
      "text": "the accomplishments --"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 55220.0,
      "end_time": 56796.0,
      "text": "they fade."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 56820.0,
      "end_time": 60236.0,
      "text": "But the hardest nights of my life have stuck with me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 60260.0,
      "end_time": 62756.0,
      "text": "impacting who I am"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 62780.0,
      "end_time": 64500.0,
      "text": "and what I do."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 65180.00000000001,
      "end_time": 71380.0,
      "text": "In 2010, my third son, Joel, was diagnosed with a rare and aggressive brain tumor."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 72300.0,
      "end_time": 74235.0,
      "text": "And before that year was finished,"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 74260.0,
      "end_time": 76796.0,
      "text": "doctors sat my husband and I down"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 76820.0,
      "end_time": 80760.0,
      "text": "and let us know that his tumor had returned"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 80100.0,
      "end_time": 84820.0,
      "text": "despite the most aggressive chemotherapy and radiation that they could offer him."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 85900.0,
      "end_time": 87796.0,
      "text": "On that terrible night,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 87820.0,
      "end_time": 91916.0,
      "text": "after learning that Joel had perhaps four months to live,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 91940.0,
      "end_time": 94795.0,
      "text": "I cuddled up with my two older sons in bed --"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 94820.0,
      "end_time": 97356.0,
      "text": "they were five and three at the time --"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 97380.0,
      "end_time": 100476.0,
      "text": "and I never really knew how much they understood,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 100500.0,
      "end_time": 104196.0,
      "text": "so I started telling them a bedtime story."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 104220.0,
      "end_time": 108760.0,
      "text": "I told them about this very brave knight named Joel"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 108100.0,
      "end_time": 112740.0,
      "text": "and his adventure fighting a terrible dragon called cancer."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 113540.0,
      "end_time": 116596.0,
      "text": "Every night, I told them more of the story,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 116620.0,
      "end_time": 118636.0,
      "text": "but I never let the story end."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 118660.0,
      "end_time": 121795.0,
      "text": "I was just building up a context that they could understand"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 121820.0,
      "end_time": 124760.0,
      "text": "and hoping that our prayers would be answered"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 124100.0,
      "end_time": 126595.0,
      "text": "and I would never have to tell them that that knight,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 126620.0,
      "end_time": 128916.0,
      "text": "who had fought so bravely,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 128940.0,
      "end_time": 130476.0,
      "text": "was done fighting"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 130500.0,
      "end_time": 132780.0,
      "text": "and could rest now, forever."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 134260.0,
      "end_time": 138756.0,
      "text": "Fortunately, I never did have to finish that bedtime story."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 138780.0,
      "end_time": 140956.0,
      "text": "My children outgrew it."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 140980.0,
      "end_time": 145760.0,
      "text": "Joel responded better than anyone expected to palliative treatment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 145100.0,
      "end_time": 146756.0,
      "text": "and so instead of months,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 146780.0,
      "end_time": 153600.0,
      "text": "we spent years learning how to love our dying child with all of our hearts."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 153900.0,
      "end_time": 156436.0,
      "text": "Learning to recognize that shameful feeling"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 156460.0,
      "end_time": 159356.0,
      "text": "of holding back just a little love"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 159380.0,
      "end_time": 162236.0,
      "text": "to try to spare ourselves just a little pain"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 162260.0,
      "end_time": 164820.0,
      "text": "somewhere further down the road."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 165580.0,
      "end_time": 168360.0,
      "text": "We pushed past that self-preservation"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 168600.0,
      "end_time": 172980.0,
      "text": "because Joel was worth loving even if that love could crush us."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 174200.0,
      "end_time": 178460.0,
      "text": "And that lesson of intense vulnerability has changed me ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 179260.0,
      "end_time": 181820.0,
      "text": "more than any award ever could."
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 182220.0,
      "end_time": 185556.0,
      "text": "We started living like Joel could live,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 185580.0,
      "end_time": 190820.0,
      "text": "and we began developing a video game called \"That Dragon, Cancer.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 191740.0,
      "end_time": 193860.0,
      "text": "It was the story of Joel."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 194580.0,
      "end_time": 198760.0,
      "text": "It was the story of hope in the shadow of death."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 198100.0,
      "end_time": 199620.0,
      "text": "It was the story of faith"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 200460.0,
      "end_time": 201916.0,
      "text": "and doubt,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 201940.0,
      "end_time": 207600.0,
      "text": "and the realization that a wrestle with doubt is a part of faith --"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 207940.0,
      "end_time": 209500.0,
      "text": "maybe the biggest part of it."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 210380.0,
      "end_time": 213835.0,
      "text": "It was a story that began as a miracle"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 213860.0,
      "end_time": 216300.0,
      "text": "and ended as a memorial."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 217660.0,
      "end_time": 219756.0,
      "text": "(Music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 219780.0,
      "end_time": 221360.0,
      "text": "(Giggle)"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 221600.0,
      "end_time": 222396.0,
      "text": "(Clapping)"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 222420.0,
      "end_time": 225995.0,
      "text": "(Music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 226200.0,
      "end_time": 229760.0,
      "text": "(Video) Dad: Bouncing around, do you like that?"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 229100.0,
      "end_time": 230316.0,
      "text": "(Giggle)"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 230340.0,
      "end_time": 231556.0,
      "text": "I love your giggle."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 231580.0,
      "end_time": 233740.0,
      "text": "(Music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 238140.0,
      "end_time": 239579.0,
      "text": "(Giggle)"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 241420.0,
      "end_time": 246179.0,
      "text": "[A Journey of Hope In the Shadow of Death]"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 247100.0,
      "end_time": 250116.0,
      "text": "[That Dragon, Cancer]"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 250140.0,
      "end_time": 253220.0,
      "text": "(Music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 255380.0,
      "end_time": 257276.0,
      "text": "When you play \"That Dragon, Cancer,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 257300.0,
      "end_time": 261276.0,
      "text": "you&#39;re transformed into a witness of Joel&#39;s life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 261300.0,
      "end_time": 263476.0,
      "text": "exploring an emotional landscape,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 263500.0,
      "end_time": 269360.0,
      "text": "clicking to discover more of what we as a family felt and experienced."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 269600.0,
      "end_time": 273596.0,
      "text": "It feels a little bit like analyzing interactive poetry"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 273620.0,
      "end_time": 275956.0,
      "text": "because every game mechanic is a metaphor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 275980.0,
      "end_time": 278356.0,
      "text": "and so the more the player asks themselves"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 278380.0,
      "end_time": 282316.0,
      "text": "what we as designers were trying to express and why,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 282340.0,
      "end_time": 284700.0,
      "text": "the richer the experience becomes."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 285220.0,
      "end_time": 288236.0,
      "text": "We took that vulnerability that Joel taught us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 288260.0,
      "end_time": 290820.0,
      "text": "and we encoded the game with it."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 291340.0,
      "end_time": 294916.0,
      "text": "Players expect their video games to offer them branching narrative"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 294940.0,
      "end_time": 298476.0,
      "text": "so that every decision that they make feels important"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 298500.0,
      "end_time": 301196.0,
      "text": "and can change the outcome of the game."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 301220.0,
      "end_time": 303996.0,
      "text": "We subverted that principle of game design,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 304200.0,
      "end_time": 307395.0,
      "text": "collapsing the choices in on the player"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 307420.0,
      "end_time": 309196.0,
      "text": "so that they discover for themselves"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 309220.0,
      "end_time": 313420.0,
      "text": "that there is nothing that they can do that will change the outcome for Joel."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 314100.0,
      "end_time": 319876.0,
      "text": "And they feel that discovery as deeply and desperately as we felt it"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 319900.0,
      "end_time": 324750.0,
      "text": "on nights when we held Joel in our arms praying for hours,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 324100.0,
      "end_time": 329540.0,
      "text": "stubbornly holding out hope for a grace that we could not create for ourselves."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 330780.0,
      "end_time": 332140.0,
      "text": "We&#39;d all prefer to win,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 332980.0,
      "end_time": 335340.0,
      "text": "but when you discover that you can&#39;t win,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 336380.0,
      "end_time": 338200.0,
      "text": "what do you value instead?"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 339420.0,
      "end_time": 341636.0,
      "text": "I never planned to write video games,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 341660.0,
      "end_time": 344196.0,
      "text": "but these moments that really change our lives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 344220.0,
      "end_time": 348340.0,
      "text": "they often come as the result of our hardship -- and not our glory."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 349340.0,
      "end_time": 351436.0,
      "text": "When we thought that Joel could live,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 351460.0,
      "end_time": 353596.0,
      "text": "I left the game designing to my husband."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 353620.0,
      "end_time": 355676.0,
      "text": "I chimed in here and there"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 355700.0,
      "end_time": 358676.0,
      "text": "with a scene or two and some suggestions."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 358700.0,
      "end_time": 361340.0,
      "text": "But after the night that Joel died,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 362300.0,
      "end_time": 363716.0,
      "text": "the passion,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 363740.0,
      "end_time": 367916.0,
      "text": "the possibility of sharing Joel&#39;s life through our video game --"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 367940.0,
      "end_time": 370760.0,
      "text": "it was something that I couldn&#39;t resist."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 370100.0,
      "end_time": 371436.0,
      "text": "I started writing more,"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 371460.0,
      "end_time": 373876.0,
      "text": "I sat in on our team&#39;s design meetings,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 373900.0,
      "end_time": 376996.0,
      "text": "I added more ideas and I helped direct scenes."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 377200.0,
      "end_time": 381916.0,
      "text": "And I discovered that creating a video game is telling a story,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 381940.0,
      "end_time": 384676.0,
      "text": "but with an entirely new vocabulary."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 384700.0,
      "end_time": 390236.0,
      "text": "All the same elements of imagination and symbolism are there,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 390260.0,
      "end_time": 392876.0,
      "text": "but they&#39;re just partnered with player agency"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 392900.0,
      "end_time": 394900.0,
      "text": "and system responsiveness."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 395900.0,
      "end_time": 397556.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s challenging work."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 397580.0,
      "end_time": 400596.0,
      "text": "I have to think in a totally new way to do it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 400620.0,
      "end_time": 402276.0,
      "text": "but I love it."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 402300.0,
      "end_time": 404900.0,
      "text": "And I wouldn&#39;t have known that without Joel."
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 406100.0,
      "end_time": 408396.0,
      "text": "Maybe you&#39;re a little surprised"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 408420.0,
      "end_time": 413500.0,
      "text": "by our choice to share our story of terminal cancer through a video game."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 414180.0,
      "end_time": 417516.0,
      "text": "Perhaps you&#39;re even thinking like so many people before you:"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 417540.0,
      "end_time": 419860.0,
      "text": "cancer is not a game."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 421100.0,
      "end_time": 423276.0,
      "text": "Well, tell that to any pediatric cancer parent"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 423300.0,
      "end_time": 427236.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s ever taken an exam glove and blown it up into a balloon,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 427260.0,
      "end_time": 429996.0,
      "text": "or transformed a syringe into a rocket ship,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 430200.0,
      "end_time": 434156.0,
      "text": "or let their child ride their IV pole through the hospital halls"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 434180.0,
      "end_time": 435860.0,
      "text": "like it was a race car."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 436700.0,
      "end_time": 438796.0,
      "text": "Because when you have children,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 438820.0,
      "end_time": 440659.0,
      "text": "everything is a game."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 441460.0,
      "end_time": 445395.0,
      "text": "And when your young child experiences something traumatic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 445420.0,
      "end_time": 449476.0,
      "text": "you work even harder to make sure that their life feels like a game"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 449500.0,
      "end_time": 453380.0,
      "text": "because children naturally explore their worlds through play."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 454140.0,
      "end_time": 457750.0,
      "text": "While cancer can steal many things from a family,"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 457100.0,
      "end_time": 458700.0,
      "text": "it shouldn&#39;t steal play."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 459700.0,
      "end_time": 463276.0,
      "text": "If you&#39;re listening to me and you&#39;re trying to imagine this family"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 463300.0,
      "end_time": 467516.0,
      "text": "that revolves entirely around a dying child,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 467540.0,
      "end_time": 471556.0,
      "text": "and you can&#39;t imagine joy as part of that picture,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 471580.0,
      "end_time": 474635.0,
      "text": "then we were right to share our story with you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 474660.0,
      "end_time": 478316.0,
      "text": "because that season of our life was hard."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 478340.0,
      "end_time": 481116.0,
      "text": "Unspeakably hard at times,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 481140.0,
      "end_time": 483219.0,
      "text": "but it was also pure hope,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 483820.0,
      "end_time": 485436.0,
      "text": "deep love"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 485460.0,
      "end_time": 488340.0,
      "text": "and joy like I have never experienced since."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 489540.0,
      "end_time": 493676.0,
      "text": "Our video game was our attempt to share that world"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 493700.0,
      "end_time": 495916.0,
      "text": "with people who hadn&#39;t experienced it before,"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 495940.0,
      "end_time": 499740.0,
      "text": "because we never could imagine that world until it became ours."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 501200.0,
      "end_time": 504600.0,
      "text": "We made a video game that&#39;s hard to play."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 505180.0,
      "end_time": 507436.0,
      "text": "It will never be a blockbuster."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 507460.0,
      "end_time": 511195.0,
      "text": "People have to prepare themselves to invest emotionally"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 511220.0,
      "end_time": 514740.0,
      "text": "in a story that they know will break their hearts."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 515700.00000000006,
      "end_time": 518360.00000000006,
      "text": "But when our hearts break,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 518590.00000000006,
      "end_time": 520380.00000000006,
      "text": "they heal a little differently."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 521820.00000000006,
      "end_time": 526715.0,
      "text": "My broken heart has been healing with a new and a deeper compassion --"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 526739.0,
      "end_time": 529676.0,
      "text": "a desire to sit with people in their pain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 529700.0,
      "end_time": 532715.0,
      "text": "to hear their stories and try to help tell them"
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 532739.0,
      "end_time": 534700.0,
      "text": "so that they know that they&#39;re seen."
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 536420.0,
      "end_time": 540756.0,
      "text": "On the night when \"That Dragon, Cancer\" won the Game for Impact Award,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 540780.0,
      "end_time": 542196.0,
      "text": "we cheered,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 542220.0,
      "end_time": 545396.0,
      "text": "we smiled and we talked about Joel"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 545420.0,
      "end_time": 547675.0,
      "text": "and the impact he had on our life --"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 547700.0,
      "end_time": 551796.0,
      "text": "on all of those hard and hopeful nights that we shared with him"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 551820.0,
      "end_time": 553276.0,
      "text": "when he changed our hearts"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 553300.0,
      "end_time": 559180.0,
      "text": "and taught us so much more about life and love and faith and purpose."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 560380.0,
      "end_time": 566140.0,
      "text": "That award will never mean as much to me as even a single photograph of my son,"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 567200.0,
      "end_time": 571675.0,
      "text": "but it does represent all of the people who his life has impacted,"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 571700.0,
      "end_time": 573796.0,
      "text": "people I&#39;ll never meet."
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 573820.0,
      "end_time": 576180.0,
      "text": "They write me emails sometimes."
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 576700.0,
      "end_time": 582156.0,
      "text": "They tell me that they miss Joel, even though they never met him."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 582180.0,
      "end_time": 586819.0,
      "text": "They describe the tears that they&#39;ve shed for my son,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 587740.0,
      "end_time": 591556.0,
      "text": "and it makes my burden of grief just a little bit lighter"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 591580.0,
      "end_time": 593676.0,
      "text": "knowing that it&#39;s shared with a 10-year-old"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 593700.0,
      "end_time": 595716.0,
      "text": "watching a YouTube playthrough,"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 595740.0,
      "end_time": 599956.0,
      "text": "or a doctor playing on his airplane with a smartphone,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 599980.0,
      "end_time": 605420.0,
      "text": "or a professor introducing Joel to her first-year philosophy students."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 606620.0,
      "end_time": 610220.0,
      "text": "We made a video game that&#39;s hard to play."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 611100.0,
      "end_time": 614360.0,
      "text": "But that feels just right to me,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 614600.0,
      "end_time": 616636.0,
      "text": "because the hardest moments of our lives"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 616660.0,
      "end_time": 620140.0,
      "text": "change us more than any goal we could ever accomplish."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 621140.0,
      "end_time": 623795.0,
      "text": "Tragedy has shifted my heart"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 623820.0,
      "end_time": 626860.0,
      "text": "more than any dream I could ever see come true."
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 627940.0,
      "end_time": 629156.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 629180.0,
      "end_time": 633418.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}